 Gibbs sampling steps: the 
\emph on
positive phase
\emph default
, where 
\begin_inset Formula $P(\mathbf{S=s}\mid\mathbf{V=v})s_{i}s_{j}$
\end_inset

 is approximated, and the 
\emph on
negative phase
\emph default
